snippet.title: Hunters Gate - Daydream VR game
snippet.description:
Hunters Gate is a fast paced, arcade shooter in the vein of games like Gauntlet and Smash TV. The town of Hunters Gate is under attack from Hell and its up to 'Guns for Hire' Forge and Payne to take back the town and ultimately take the fight to the underworld.

Hunters Gate is available exclusively on Daydream.

Buy Game Now - https://goo.gl/VEw0cN
